  "text": "Hi {{first_name}},\n\nwe processed your refund for {{product_name}}. Most banks post the credit within {{refund_timing}}.\n\nRefund amount: {{amount_refunded}}\nRefund ID: {{refund_id}}\nOriginal payment: {{original_payment_date}}\nExpected timing: {{refund_timing}}\n\nView billing history: {{billing_history_url}}\n\nIf the credit does not appear after the expected timing, your bank can trace it using the refund ID.",
  "mjml": "<mjml>\n  <mj-head>\n    <mj-title>Refund Processed</mj-title>\n    <mj-preview>A calm refund confirmation email with premium customer-care positioning.</mj-preview>\n    <mj-attributes>\n      <mj-all font-family=\"-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif\" />\n      <mj-text color=\"#181229\" font-size=\"16px\" line-height=\"24px\" />\n      <mj-section padding=\"0\" />\n      <mj-button border-radius=\"999px\" font-size=\"15px\" font-weight=\"800\" inner-padding=\"15px 24px\" />\n    </mj-attributes>\n  </mj-head>\n  <mj-body background-color=\"#f5f3ff\" width=\"600px\">\n    <mj-section padding=\"28px 22px 14px\">\n      <mj-column>\n        <mj-text align=\"center\" color=\"#625a72\" font-size=\"12px\" font-weight=\"800\" letter-spacing=\"1.8px\" text-transform=\"uppercase\">{{product_name}}</mj-text>\n      </mj-column>\n    </mj-section>\n    <mj-section background-color=\"#1e123b\" border-radius=\"22px 22px 0 0\" padding=\"34px 34px 28px\">\n      <mj-column>\n        <mj-text color=\"#8b5cf6\" font-size=\"11px\" font-weight=\"900\" letter-spacing=\"2px\" text-transform=\"uppercase\" padding=\"0 0 14px\">Refund processed</mj-text>\n        <mj-text color=\"#ffffff\" font-size=\"30px\" font-weight=\"850\" line-height=\"36px\" padding=\"0 0 12px\">{{amount_refunded}} is on its way back</mj-text>\n        <mj-text color=\"#ffffff\" font-size=\"15px\" line-height=\"24px\" padding=\"0\">Hi {{first_name}}, we processed your refund for {{product_name}}. Most banks post the credit within {{refund_timing}}.</mj-text>\n      </mj-column>\n    </mj-section>\n    <mj-section background-color=\"#ffffff\" border-radius=\"0 0 22px 22px\" padding=\"0 30px 30px\">\n      <mj-column>\n        <mj-spacer height=\"26px\" />\n        <mj-text background-color=\"#ede9fe\" color=\"#181229\" font-size=\"13px\" font-weight=\"800\" line-height=\"20px\" padding=\"18px 20px 4px\">Refund amount</mj-text>\n        <mj-text background-color=\"#ede9fe\" color=\"#181229\" font-size=\"28px\" font-weight=\"900\" line-height=\"34px\" padding=\"0 20px 18px\">{{amount_refunded}}</mj-text>\n        <mj-table padding=\"22px 0 4px\">\n          <tr><td style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd6fe;color:#625a72;font-size:13px;\">Refund ID</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd6fe;color:#181229;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;\">{{refund_id}}</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd6fe;color:#625a72;font-size:13px;\">Original payment</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd6fe;color:#181229;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;\">{{original_payment_date}}</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd6fe;color:#625a72;font-size:13px;\">Expected timing</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd6fe;color:#181229;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;\">{{refund_timing}}</td></tr>\n        </mj-table>\n        <mj-button href=\"{{billing_history_url}}\" background-color=\"#8b5cf6\" color=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"26px 0 8px\">View billing history</mj-button>\n        <mj-text align=\"center\" color=\"#625a72\" font-size=\"13px\" line-height=\"20px\" padding=\"18px 10px 0\">If the credit does not appear after the expected timing, your bank can trace it using the refund ID.</mj-text>\n      </mj-column>\n    </mj-section>\n    <mj-section padding=\"22px 20px 40px\">\n      <mj-column>\n        <mj-text align=\"center\" color=\"#625a72\" font-size=\"12px\" line-height=\"18px\">TemplateForge marketplace template. Update branding and URLs before production use.</mj-text>\n      </mj-column>\n    </mj-section>\n  </mj-body>\n</mjml>",
